{"tid":139092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉咁有能力都入唔到閘，香港玩完","createTime":"2017-03-01T06:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T07:20:16.000Z","uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a010ef7eb8a42270604913846be0b531c6ae799","tid":139092,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"莊增：hea友，唔識講野，公共政策演說力低下，無料到<br />\n<br />\n胡官：成世做法官，俾人奉承慣，唔識協調唔識管理唔識公共政策，成世活係象牙塔到，識條春俗務咩，識條然做特首<br />\n<br />\n林鄭：剛復自用，無協調力，自以為「好打得」上身，而且推御責任，永遠唔覺得自己錯，胸襟不足，無容人之量。話唔選特首，但結果反口覆舌，自命清高，事實係靠邊站，其人不可信也<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而葉劉做官多年，深受下屬愛戴，能力有目共睹。廿三條衰左，自承惡果，辭官讀書（林鄭政改推唔到，國教推唔到，又唔見有人孭飛辭職，講豁達，講氣節，同葉劉差好遠），好有擔當。之後又透過直選入立法會。一個由高官，落返去地區，都見到葉劉有心有力有擔當，今日落得只有廿幾張選票既下場，真係令人唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對比起葉劉，其他三個候選人真係垃圾都不如"},{"pid":"31515767a4c70944164dd480e4aa584c0bc4191f","tid":139092,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都是屎 比甚麼"},{"pid":"965bbe2744af229d07b7d684943b77dcc3d61fae","tid":139092,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"負評我既夠唔夠18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e11a1d29be3f25b35f10ef8d2852d2bd445a07f","tid":139092,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評我既夠唔夠18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3fe9caf922c67a63bec4e1cad5da4d13b10e8f","tid":139092,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"葉太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8c0cbd911ee78088af97933d9cba49fa75fdf8","tid":139092,"uid":78379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"講勢力，財力。<br />\n能力有什麼能有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4108bba78003962672280334dcf7961e4735eae","tid":139092,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講勢力，財力。<br />\n能力有什麼能有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講錢就掂，中國就唔會只係中國啦"}]}